:7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"9 月9人權法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n「懷疑有組織發佈大量fake news想搞散場抗爭」<br />\n小心分清楚真與假！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMKxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=85d1cb9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"723a6bdf12724d905091322b4a35cc686c0b8aed","tid":1552913,"uid":255121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f2ddc445c15d28c2495b3d421a7ef1b8046e3d6","tid":1552913,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f87cebc588804cfd4fab5caa7534bc74bb32e5dc","tid":1552913,"uid":13349,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"第一句就be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"天意如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm